      "role": "Wealth Operations Specialist agent for the Wealth Client Onboarding Orchestrator workflow",
      "primaryObjective": "Validates account applications against custodian requirements before submission and routes corrected forms through DocuSign. Tracks every onboarding milestone including ACAT transfers, publishing live status to Salesforce for the advisor and client portal. so the Wealth Operations Specialist can move the Days from signed agreement to funded account KPI.",
